source.name: Appropriation Figures for the Antitrust Division, Fiscal Years 1903-2012
source.description: This dataset contains five elements for appropriation figures for the Antitrust Division from 1903 to present. - Fiscal year - Direct Appropriation Amount Included in Appropriations Bill ($ in thousands) - Filing Fee Revenue Amount Included in Appropriations Bill ($ in thousands)  - Total Funding Appropriated ($ in thousands)  - Notes
